==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hele
<hw>Hele</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>helan</ets>, akin to D.
<ets>helen</ets>, OHG. <ets>helan</ets>, G. <ets>hehlen</ets>, L.
<ets>celare</ets>. ⟦root⟧17. See <er>Hell</er>, and cf.
<er>Conceal</er>.]</ety> <def>To hide; to cover; to roof.</def>
